{"tid":1746572,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"Once you go black 打卡陳XX","createTime":"2019-11-22T20:06:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T09:07:00.000Z","uid":327909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"36f9b745afc17b553e8a88afde4e2480d05b75da","tid":1746572,"uid":327909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T20:06:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KTYxj4Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKTYxj4Y.jpg&h=884e1b82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n之前發夢時聽返泥，有個手足同我講佢老豆(有老黑背景) 爆料疑當區議員用一百萬賄賂富泰邨某泰樓互助委員會，為其區議會選舉助選。。。<br />\n<br />\n有個住左十幾年的富泰街坊已經證實左！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QCs6pvs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQCs6pvs.jpg&h=2bd918b9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n <br />\n綽號：傻輝  某泰樓互委會副主席<br />\n<ins>各位<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">汕尾人</span></strong> 你收齊錢未啊？！！</ins><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：<br />\n<br />\n汕尾同鄉會請願 撐「明日大嶼」計劃 2018-10-23<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcd.com/content/2018-10/23/content_1106121.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcd.com%2Fcontent%2F2018-10%2F23%2Fcontent_1106121.html&d=ZU5rKlsKhNp37FgV%2FTwvgnjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=17a57fb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcd.com/content/2018-10/23/content_1106121.html</a><br />\n<br />\n屯門區議會禁團體直播大嶼會議 市民：有知情權 議員：阻全世界 2019-03-05 <a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/18%E5%8D%80%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/302424/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E7%A6%81%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD%E5%A4%A7%E5%B6%BC%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0-%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91-%E6%9C%89%E7%9F%A5%E6%83%85%E6%AC%8A-%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1-%E9%98%BB%E5%85%A8%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F18%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F302424%2F%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%25A6%2581%25E5%259C%2598%25E9%25AB%2594%25E7%259B%25B4%25E6%2592%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B6%25BC%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25AD%25B0-%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591-%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%259F%25A5%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%25AC%258A-%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1-%25E9%2598%25BB%25E5%2585%25A8%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C&d=ZU5rKlsKhNp37FgV%2FTwvgnjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=ecc65fbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/18%E5%8D%80%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/302424/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E7%A6%81%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD%E5%A4%A7%E5%B6%BC%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0-%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91-%E6%9C%89%E7%9F%A5%E6%83%85%E6%AC%8A-%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1-%E9%98%BB%E5%85%A8%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C</a><br />\n<br />\n工聯會富泰區議員陳文偉斥拍攝市民：「請你哋離開，呢度係旁聽席，唔係請願區，你哋𠵱家阻住全世界。」他更一度要求閉門會議。而民建聯兆翠區議員葉文斌亦多次要求市民停止拍攝及直播，「表達完意見，請你離開，你𠵱家浪費梗市民公帑。」拍攝的市民則回應指：「呢件事（明日大嶼）關乎全港市民，我哋覺得市民有知情權。」<br />\n<br />\n「明日大嶼」屯門區諮詢遇狙擊叫停<br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20190306/mobile/odn-20190306-0306_00176_035.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190306%2Fmobile%2Fodn-20190306-0306_00176_035.html&d=ZU5rKlsKhNp37FgV%2FTwvgnjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=2af6a33f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20190306/mobile/odn-20190306-0306_00176_035.html</a><br />\n<br />\n相關報道：【屯門區議會有幾兇？報警驅趕東大嶼示威和直播區議會的市民離場】2019-03-07<br />\n<a href=\"https://grassmediaction.wordpress.com/2019/03/07/%E3%80%90%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E6%9C%89%E5%B9%BE%E5%85%87%EF%BC%9F%E5%A0%B1%E8%AD%A6%E9%A9%85%E8%B6%95%E6%9D%B1%E5%A4%A7%E5%B6%BC%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E5%92%8C%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgrassmediaction.wordpress.com%2F2019%2F03%2F07%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25B9%25BE%25E5%2585%2587%25EF%25BC%259F%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%25A9%2585%25E8%25B6%2595%25E6%259D%25B1%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B6%25BC%25E7%25A4%25BA